reviewText: WOW I wish this  version was on DVD but thank goodness I still have my VCR, because I loved the songs and easy exercises that were  shown with each uplifting  gospell!

I have an older version of a Donna Richardson dance video, so I am familiar with Donna's style.
She is an encourager.....goes slow enough for me to catch the steps pretty quickly, but fast enough
that it's fun, aerobic exercise!
